// atomicGL
//----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// author: RC				
// contact: cozot@irisa.fr
// version: 0.1
// current version date: 2015/09/05
//----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// atomicGL
//----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// TODO list
